data.description: DeWitt schools and in the highly sought-after Duxbury Estates sub. Beautiful  5 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, finished basement with egress windows, all on nearly an acre!  Convenient to 69, close to schools and shopping.  Open floor plan, plenty of natural light and many updates: Including- roof, furnace, AC, vinyl siding, water heater, water softener/filtration system, vinyl flooring on main level, recently stained deck with custom-built pergola.  Gorgeous primary suite with eclectic tile, tub/shower and spacious walk-in closet. First floor laundry room.  Lower level features 2 Rec Room areas, 5th bedroom with attached full bath. 3366 square feet of total living space! Attached 3 car garage. All baths have been updated. All this and more!
